name: Inner /ˈfiːlɪŋ/
description: "Our thoughts and feelings are experienced as distinct from the rest of us. It's like an intentional optical illusion. This fallacy is like a cage for us, confining us to our own desires and affection for only a few people close to us. Whether it's good nor bad. Bloom and be as colorful as you can. don't take the negativity take over your inner self." By @Baimtje
